  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a cast-iron skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic, lemongrass, turmeric, and cumin, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add coconut milk and fish sauce, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes, or until slightly thickened.",
    "Add shrimp and cook until pink, about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in maple syrup and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, or until the syrup is well combined with the other ingredients.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with Thai basil."
  ],
